  Update Model Permissions

› 1. Ask for approval  Mantis can read and edit files in the current
                       workspace, and run commands. Approval is required to
                       access the internet or edit other files.
  2. Full Access       Mantis can edit files outside this workspace and access
                       the internet without asking for approval. Exercise
                       caution when using.

  Press enter to confirm or esc to go back
